{"tid":845741,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone XS LTE 網速測試 改用 Intel 兩年網速能抵高通嗎？","createTime":"2018-10-03T01:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T11:31:14.000Z","uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"409858e57a1056c4599f5dc9d099f2b4e91ac644","tid":845741,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:48:07.000Z","msg":"iPhone XS 改用 4&times;4 MIMO 配 Intel 晶片，但開售之初不少人投訴其流動網絡和 WiFi 收發不良。當然，這可能是頭一批貨的瑕疵問題，如果對比其他 iPhone 和 Android 手機，iPhone XS 的網速表現如何？<br />\n<br />\n最近美國 PCMag 網站在不同 LTE 收發度之下測試 iPhone XS、iPhone X、Galaxy Note 9 和 Pixel 2 的下載網速，iPhone XS 和 iPhone X 使用 Intel 晶片，Galaxy Note 9 和 Pixel 2 使用高通晶片，測試環境是 AT&amp;T、T0-Mobile、Verizon 等美國和加拿大主要營運商使用的 Band 4 20MHz 頻譜。<br />\n<br />\n結果可見 iPhone XS 使用 Intel 7560 網絡基帶晶片配合 4&times;4 MIMO 之下，在 -85dBm 的訊號之下，下載網速明顯比 iPhone X 快 1 倍，達 400Mbps，但在 -100dBm 上下的整體網速只能追貼 Galaxy Note 9 和 Pixel 2，並沒有超越。而 iPhone XS Max 在 -90 到 -106 之間的訊號收發比 iPhone XS 為佳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/094647_e076231a37248d15298c43269183abdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F094647_e076231a37248d15298c43269183abdd.png&h=afd106ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/094701_7f0bed517bec25e78f45c02b6d392798.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F094701_7f0bed517bec25e78f45c02b6d392798.png&h=ca96677f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n確實，iPhone XS 4x4MIMO 確實幫了 iPhone XS 網絡收發速度，然而系統更新可能會影響網速，iPhone X 在 iOS 12 更新之後，LTE 訊號在-126dBm 的情況之下突然變弱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/094718_2d6ee26d6e5926be8747fe3e75da2b06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F094718_2d6ee26d6e5926be8747fe3e75da2b06.png&h=5cfe2dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從這個測試可見，iPhone 網絡快慢似乎不受晶片品牌的支配，MIMO 制式反而有更大影響。"},{"pid":"ca94f2d7265f47ba2e9286b17e1f51d79aa3cc02","tid":845741,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:48:57.000Z","msg":"相對接收力問到，發熱耗電問題更嚴重吧"},{"pid":"88f5aed373d0230f68f59d4fb6b2233025973964","tid":845741,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"之前港版iPhone7, 8係用高通，今代係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2331b47ccefa2abd490a94afef3c5890973e27","tid":845741,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f5aed373d0230f68f59d4fb6b2233025973964","tid":845741,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"之前港版iPhone7, 8係用高通，今代係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:56.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"b98c5496f0c97130143a0019c7b9171b95bce499","tid":845741,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de99d92eed20709f97548af55a0498fee16305d","tid":845741,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f5aed373d0230f68f59d4fb6b2233025973964","tid":845741,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"之前港版iPhone7, 8係用高通，今代係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"今代統一用intel modem"},{"pid":"32ff66ad97bfd3b6f88fa6820861475c9b92c9f6","tid":845741,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8de99d92eed20709f97548af55a0498fee16305d","tid":845741,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f5aed373d0230f68f59d4fb6b2233025973964","tid":845741,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"之前港版iPhone7, 8係用高通，今代係咪？<img src=\"/as